div.div: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!

Stop-motion short in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.
Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu 3rd Season
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Psychological, Romance, Thriller

The third season of Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu. A year has passed since Subarus victory at the Sanctuary. He savors a life of fulfillment while Emilias camp stands united for the royal selectionuntil a fateful letter arrives. Anastasia, a royal selection candidate, has invited Emilia to the Watergate City of Priestella. But as the party begins its journey, crisis stirs beneath the surface and Subaru meets a cruel fate once again. (Source: Crunchyroll) Notes: The first episode has an extended runtime of ~90 minutes, and received an early premiere at Anime Expo on July 5, 2024.

When the duke was a young boy, a witch made it so that any living thing he touched died. Unable to cope with such a cursed child, his family sent him away to live in an old mansion. Now a young man, his only companions are an elderly butler and his childhood friend, a buxom, blonde maid named Alice. Despite the fact that touching the duke means instant death, Alice is constantly teasing him, getting close and flirting mercilessly. But even though Alice loves to make the duke blush, her affection for him is the real deal. Can the two figure out a way to break the witchs spell? (Source: Seven Seas Entertainment) Note: The chapter count includes 15 extra chapters.

Its time to change the misguided medical care in another world by using modern pharmacy!
When a young pharmacologist gives his life to his research and dies from overwork, he finds himself reincarnated as a boy named Farma, the son of the court physician. In a new world where faulty remedies run rampant, Farma uses modern pharmacy and cheat powers to cure all the diseases around him.
(Source: One Peace Books)
